\c 1
\s Umkhuleko kaNehemiya ngabeJerusalema
\p
\v 1 Amazwi kaNehemiya indodana kaHakaliya\x + 10.1.\x*. Kwasekusithi ngenyanga kaKisilevi\x + Zek. 7.1.\x* ngomnyaka wamatshumi amabili\x + 2.1.\x*, lapho mina ngiseShushani\x + Esta 1.2,5. 2.3,5,8. 3.15. 4.16. 8.14,15. 9.6,11,12,15. Dan. 8.2. Esta 11.3. 16.18. Ezra 4.9.\x* isigodlo\x + 1 Lan. 29.1.\x*,
\v 2 uHanani omunye wabafowethu wafika yena lamadoda avela koJuda\x + 7.2.\x*. Ngasengibabuza mayelana lamaJuda ayephunyukile asala ekuthunjweni, langeJerusalema.
\v 3 Basebesithi kimi: Labo abasalayo abasala ekuthunjweni lapho esabelweni baphakathi kokuhlupheka okukhulu lehlazo, lomduli weJerusalema wadilika\x + 2.13. 2 Kho. 25.10.\x*, lamasango ayo atshiswa ngomlilo\x + 2.17. 2.3,13.\x*.
\p
\v 4 Kwasekusithi sengizwe lamazwi ngahlala phansi ngakhala inyembezi, ngalila \add okw\add*ezinsuku, ngizila ukudla, ngikhuleka phambi kukaNkulunkulu wamazulu\x + Ezra 9.3.\x*.
\v 5 Ngathi: Ngiyancenga, N\nd kosi\nd*, Nkulunkulu wamazulu, Nkulunkulu omkhulu lowesabekayo\x + Dan. 9.4. Dute. 7.21.\x*, ogcina isivumelwano lomusa kulabo abamthandayo labagcina imilayo yakhe\x + Dute. 7.9.\x*,
\v 6 indlebe yakho ake ilalele\x + 1.11. 2 Lan. 6.40.\x*, lamehlo akho avuleke, ukuzwa umkhuleko wenceku yakho engiwukhuleka phambi kwakho lamuhla emini lebusuku\x + 1 Kho. 8.29. Dan. 9.18.\x*\x + 1.11. 2 Lan. 6.40.\x* ngabantwana bakoIsrayeli, inceku zakho, njalo ngivuma ngenxa yezono zabantwana bakoIsrayeli esizone kuwe\x + Ezra 10.1. Dan. 9.20.\x*. Yebo, mina lendlu kababa sonile\x + Hlab. 106.6.\x*;
\v 7 senze kubi lokwenza kubi kuwe, kasigcinanga imilayo lezimiso lezahlulelo\x + Jobe 34.31. Dan. 9.5.\x* owalaya ngakho uMozisi inceku yakho\x + Dute. 28.15.\x*.
\v 8 Ake ukhumbule ilizwi owalaya ngalo uMozisi inceku yakho usithi: \add Uba\add* lina liphambuka, mina ngizalichithachitha phakathi kwezizwe\x + Levi 26.33. Dute. 4.25-27. 28.64.\x*;
\v 9 uba lina liphendukela kimi, lilondoloza imilayo yami, liyenze\x + Levi 26.39-42. Dute. 4.29-31. 30.2,3.\x*, lanxa abaxotshiweyo benu besephethelweni lamazulu, ngizababutha besuka lapho\x + Dute. 30.4.\x* ngibaletha endaweni engiyikhethileyo ukubeka ibizo lami khona\x + Dute. 12.5.\x*.
\v 10 Laba-ke bazinceku zakho labantu bakho owabahlenga ngamandla akho amakhulu langesandla sakho esiqinileyo\x + Dute. 9.29.\x*.
\v 11 Ngiyacela, Nkosi, indlebe yakho ake ilalele umkhuleko wenceku yakho\x + 1.6.\x*, lomkhuleko wezinceku zakho eziloyisa ukwesaba ibizo lakho, ake uphumelelise inceku yakho lamuhla, uyinike izihawu phambi kwalumuntu\x + Isa. 26.8.\x*.
\p Njalo ngangingumphathi wezitsha zenkosi\x + 2.1. Gen. 40.2.\x*.